Do you have trouble sleeping or feel mentally foggy during the day? As a professional MMA fighter, Gustavo Lopez knows the importance of staying sharp and focused – something he struggled with until he discovered BrainTap. Whether he’s at home, in the gym, or traveling – BrainTap has become an essential part of Gustavo’s life and training regimen.

Hear more about his story below!

✨Why did you start braintapping? What problems have you been able to solve?

I started braintapping because I had trouble sleeping, worrying, and with mental clarity. I’ve been able to solve all of these problems with BrainTap. Life before was stressful and I had trouble sleeping, now it’s peaceful and I’m sleeping great.

✨What’s your favorite part about BrainTap?

My favorite part is the portability and how I can take it with me anywhere I go.

✨What are some of the biggest changes you’ve seen in your life since using BrainTap?

Using BrainTap has improved my sleep, reduced worry, increased mental clarity, and enhanced my overall well-being. I truly feel more calm and focused throughout my day.

 ✨What is your favorite session?

My favorite session is “Heart Coherence” by Katie Silcox.

Happy Birthday @bodystationstudio. Dnes 15.8.2023  sa oficiálne oslávil tento veľkolepý projekt, ktorý som priniesla z USA z tých najlepších holiatickych centier v Miami a v NYC. Keďže som Vegan a milujem Všetko čo je spojené s prírodou, tak tento nápad je časťou. V roku 2021 v čase lockdwnu a korony keď som prišla na SVK, keďže pandémia v štátoch bola zlá.
